1:Information:Information:
1.1:Information:Information about xbian-config:xbianinfo
2:Settings:XBian settings:
2.1:Resize SD:Expand root partition to fill SD card:changesdsize
2.2:Change Password:Change password for 'xbian' user:changexbianpass
2.3:Change Password:Change password for 'root' user:changerootpass
2.4:Set timezone:Set the default timezone:changetimezone
2.5:SSH root login:$ROOTSSHSTATUS SSH root login:changesshroot
2.6:Overclocking:Configure overclocking:changeoverclock
2.7:Licence MPG2:Insert, update or delete MPG2 license:changelicensempg2
2.8:Licence VC-1:Insert, update or delete VC1 license:changelicensevc1
2.9:Hostname:Change the default hostname:changehostname
2.10:Configure WLAN:Configure wireless network connection:changewlan
2.11:Configure LAN:Configure wired network connection:changelan
2.12:HDMI hotplug:Change the HDMI hotplug mode:changeforcehdmi
3:Packages:Packages:
3.1:Remote:Install packages from internet:remotepackages
3.2:Local:Install packages from *.tar.gz:remotepackages
4:Updates:Check for XBian updates:notimplemented
